OL,3,CLabour turmoil continues as Streeting
OL,4,Cmulls leadership challenge
OL,6,FWhile some 87 MPs have so far publicly
OL,7,Fcalled for Sir Keir's resignation,
OL,8,Fthey are not united behind a single
OL,9,Fcandidate to replace him.
OL,11,FOther figures regarded as potential
OL,12,Fchallengers include former deputy
OL,13,Fprime minister Angela Rayner, Energy
OL,14,FSecretary and former party leader Ed
OL,15,FMiliband and armed forces minister Al
OL,16,FCarns.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
