OL,3,CLabour turmoil continues as Streeting
OL,4,Cmulls leadership challenge
OL,6,FAhead of the introduction of the
OL,7,FSocial Housing Renewal Bill, intended
OL,8,Fto boost the supply of council homes,
OL,9,FSir Keir said his Government was
OL,10,F"taking responsibility, rebuilding
OL,11,Fsocial housing, and delivering the
OL,12,Fchange people voted for".
OL,14,FMeanwhile, the prospect of a return to
OL,15,FParliament for Greater Manchester
OL,16,FMayor Andy Burnham receded as more MPs
OL,17,Fdeclared they did not intend to give
OL,18,Fup their seats to allow him to contest
OL,19,Fa by-election.
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
