OL,3,CLabour turmoil continues as Streeting
OL,4,Cmulls leadership challenge
OL,6,FManchester MPs Afzal Khan and Jeff
OL,7,FSmith had been rumoured in Westminster
OL,8,Fto be willing to make way for Mr
OL,9,FBurnham.
OL,11,FBut both men expressly denied to the
OL,12,FPress Association that they were
OL,13,Fpreparing to stand down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
